لَّفَسَدَتِ ٱلْأَرْضُ وَلَٰكِنَّ ٱللَّهَ ذُو فَضْلٍ عَلَى ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"And thereupon, by God's leave, they routed them. And David slew Goliath; and God bestowed upon him dominion, and wisdom, and imparted to him the knowledge of whatever He willed. And if God had not enabled people to defend themselves against one another, corruption would surely overwhelm the earth: but God is limitless in His bounty unto all the worlds.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/258.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":87026,"position":1,"arabic":"فَهَزَمُوهُم","translation":"তারা অতঃপর পরাজিত করল তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87027,"position":2,"arabic":"بِإِذْنِ","translation":"অনুমতিক্রমে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87028,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87029,"position":4,"arabic":"وَقَتَلَ","translation":"এবং হত্যা করল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87030,"position":5,"arabic":"دَاوُۥدُ","translation":"দাঊদ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87031,"position":6,"arabic":"جَالُوتَ","translation":"জালুতকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87032,"position":7,"arabic":"وَءَاتَىٰهُ","translation":"এবং তাকে দিয়ে দিয়েছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87033,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87034,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمُلْكَ","translation":"রাজত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87035,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱلْحِكْمَةَ","translation":"ও প্রজ্ঞা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87036,"position":11,"arabic":"وَعَلَّمَهُۥ","translation":"ও তাকে শিক্ষা দিয়েছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_251_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":870